真心 我唔會想拎住佢係條街到行囉"},{"pid":"f166ae44f6374f4dce772eb228c0113bfbf88593","tid":112940,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T20:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/09/035946_12cce7d5f27f02cbb1f12cd4fb526ea0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F09%2F035946_12cce7d5f27f02cbb1f12cd4fb526ea0.jpg&h=9b47d273&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FimYJ2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFimYJ2W.jpg&h=0611d38c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18777Uu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18777Uu.jpg&h=09a7acc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推薦呢幾間畀大家<br />\n同埋我覺得d花後面塊紙咁長好撚似拜山拎去嗰啲花束<br />\n正正常常，去花墟買一紮 <br />\n幾枝紅玫瑰 加張黑色/深色花紙 一個球型咁 已經好靚"},{"pid":"c1681a4d92e08139220b51c5dc954e4e86215ab8","tid":112940,"uid":72746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n推薦呢幾間畀大家<br />\n同埋我覺得d花後面塊紙咁長好撚似拜山拎去嗰啲花束<br />\n正正常常，去花墟買一紮 <br />\n幾枝紅玫瑰 加張黑色/深色花紙 一個球型咁 已經好靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢幾間的確唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過我今年已經買左保鮮花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8edf045ecb364c42827773c30316723dd4b3b9","tid":112940,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:00:33.000Z","msg":"樓上d乾花要預幾多budget?洗唔洗$1000"}]}